{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idab87cb08-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9842"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9842"},"text":"§ 9842.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Settlement of accounts of line officers","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Comptroller General shall settle the account of a line officer of the Air Force or the Space Force for pay due the officer even if the officer cannot account for property entrusted to the officer or cannot make a monthly report or return, when the Comptroller General is satisfied that the inability to account for property or make a report or return was the result of the officer having been a prisoner, or of an accident or casualty of war.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idab87cb09-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/258/s2/b/14/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–258, § 2(b)(14)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-09-13"},"text":"Sept. 13, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/1058"},"text":"96 Stat. 1058","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/dA/tIX/s923/e/25"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title IX, § 923(e)(25)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/3820"},"text":"134 Stat. 3820","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idab87cb0a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idab87cb0b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:table","attrib":{"width":"50%","id":"idab87cb0c-3a6f-11f1-a5